Capstone Project Preliminary Analysis Template

Name:

Project Title: This can be a working title.

Project Objective: What is the goal? What problem are you trying to solve? Who will be your audience?

Data Collection Source:  Describe how the data was collected. Include website links. 

Methodology: Describe your preprocessing techniques. How was the data organized? What was the workflow? What tools were used to organize and better understand the data? How was the data cleaned? Were there any typos? How was this corrected? Any data type conversions, e.g. string to date values? Any other formatting, e.g. renaming columns or values?  Were any missing values replaced? If so, describe why? How will replacing the values impact the analysis? Are there any exclusions (columns, rows, or values)? Include any other methods in processing and organizing the data.

Findings: 
1.	Data Size: How many rows and columns? 
2.	Missing Values: How many? Will these need to be replaced or deleted?
3.	Duplicates:  Describe how this was detected
4.	Dates: What is the date range? Will this need to be modified for the project?
5.	Additional Findings: Identify any other findings or errors in the data. Any outliers? Any inconsistencies relative to the project?


Attach any SQL or Python code in a separate file

